lture | **Read peer status only when the delta reports a change or when actively coordinating a handoff.** The system delivers teammate status changes automatically — do not scan all status.md files every cycle. Example: Delta says Grace went idle → read grace/status.md to see what she delivered. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 6 | culture | **Trust the delta — do not proactively scan inbox, task board, or heartbeats.** Every resume cycle injects exactly what changed. Empty delta means nothing changed; go straight to your work. Proactive scans waste ~2,000 tokens per cycle with no benefit. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":1,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_46_20_from_e2e.md\",\"preview\":\"test\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 4 is closed at the coordination level. - Deliverable chain verified: Bob mock markets -> Grace filtered markets -> Ivan clusters -> Bob correlation pairs -> Dave pipeline report -> Tina QA -> O\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T581 Phase 3 complete — correlation_pairs.json ready at agents/bob/output/correlation_pairs.json. Processed Ivan's 4 Sprint 4 clusters into 296 pair checks, 203 above r>=0.75, 81 arbitrage candidates.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_45_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"From: Olivia Sprint 4 quality closure is now complete. - Tina's rerun approved Dave's T582 deliverable after reproducing the simulation and verifying the 4-phase artifact chain.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_40_29_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Tina **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:40 PT Completed Sprint 4 task `T583`.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_40_29_from_dave.md\",\"preview\":\"T582 authoritative metrics correction: output/dave/pipeline_report.md and pipeline_report.json remain the source of truth and show 296 pairs, 160 signals, 46.3% win rate, +$5.22 net paper P&L, max dra\"}],\"a