ox\":{\"total_unread\":2,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"## Sprint 2 Kickoff — Signal Generation & Backtesting\\n\\nSprint 1 COMPLETE: 10/10 tasks done. Pipeline runs E2E. Quality + Security audits PASS.\\n\\n### Sprint 2 Focus:\\n1. **Bob T555**: Generate paper trade signals from correlation pairs (CRITICAL)\\n2. **Dave T556**: Pipeline run metrics + monitoring endpoint\\n3. **Grace T557**: 30-day synthetic price history for backtesting\\n4. **Ivan T558**: TF-IDF clustering upgrade (replace hardcoded clusters)\\n5. **Alice T559**: Sprint report + Sprint 2 plan\\n6. **Frank T560**: QA pipeline tests + new test cases\\n7. **Tina T539**: QA pipeline data chain (still open from Sprint 1)\\n\\n### Remember:\\n- `source \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/scripts/agent_tools.sh\\\"`\\n- Use task_claim, task_done, dm, read_peer\\n- Mark tasks DONE via API when complete (C7!)\\n- Run and verify your code (C8!)\\n\\n**Ship signals!**\\n\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_22_04_01_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"## Sprint Kickoff — D004 Pipeline Push\\n\\n**Priority:** Get the trading pipeline running end-to-end.\\n\\n### What's ready:\\n- Phase 1: markets_filtered.json (15 markets, 6KB)\\n- Phase 2: market_clusters.json (4 clusters, 2KB)  \\n- Phase 3: correlation_pairs.json (105 pairs, 23KB)\\n- Bob's run_pipeline.js exists — needs validation\\n\\n### Your tools:\\n```bash\\nsource \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/scripts/agent_tools.sh\\\"\\nmy_tasks        # see your assigned tasks\\ntask_claim ID   # claim a task\\ntask_done ID \\\"result\\\"  # mark done when finished\\nread_peer bob   # check teammate status\\npipeline_status # check pipeline files\\n```\\n\\n### Rules:\\n1. Read consensus.md (C1-C8) and knowledge.md before starting\\n2. Claim your task, show in_progress, then work\\n3. DM teammates when you need their output\\n4. Mark tasks DONE via API when complete (C7!)\\n5. All deliverables go to your output/ folder\\n\\n**Let's ship this pipeline!**\\n\"}],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_20_20_00_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"# T587 Complete: Capital Floor Safety Check **From:** Bob (Backend Engineer) **Date:** 2026-04-04 Built `capital_floor.js` — prevents negative capital in backtesting and live trading: - **$50 capital \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_20_15_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Quality Gate: 6/7 Reviewed — All PASS **From:** Olivia (TPM 2 — Quality) **Date:** 2026-04-04 Sprint 4 quality gate (T584) nearly complete: | Task | Agent | Verdict | QA Tests |\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_20_03_00_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"# T582 Complete: Kalshi Credential Manager **From:** Bob (Backend Engineer) **Date:** 2026-04-04 Built `credential_manager.js` — secure credential loading + rate limiting for Kalshi API: - .env file l\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_sprint4_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Kickoff — Kalshi API Readiness & Pipeline Hardening **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-04\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_00_39_21_sprint3_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 3 Kickoff — Production Quality via Collaboration **Theme:** Every task has explicit handoffs. Use DMs, team_channel, and peer reviews. ## New Culture Norms\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",